hole world\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic principles\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hope that people will stop bullying, and I hope we will not see similar attacks in future Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"similar attacks\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"future Olympics\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Algerian boxer Imane Khelif claimed gold in the 66kg division and insisted afterwards: \\\"I am fully qualified to take part in this competition - I am a woman\\\"\\ud83d\\udcf1 Report:https://t.co/89g4ycyVHxpic.twitter.com/ZMExAUgA4Z The claim by her first opponent, Angela Carini, that she \\\"had never been hit so hard\\\" in the course of her 46-second defeat was seized upon by many public figures, including Donald Trump, Elon Musk and JK Rowling.\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2172, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.7358297129125879, \"rank\": 0.315273071113726, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"h